room_title: Escape room "The Dig" by Dare 2 Escape in Orlando
room_address: 5041 W Irlo Bronson Memorial Hwy Kissimmee, FL 34746
room_description:
In the heart of the Northern Sahara Desert, a famed archaeologist Dr. Eleanor Harding made a groundbreaking discovery of a full dinosaur skeleton not yet known to science. Realizing she might be on the brink of uncovering a new species, she contacted your team of elite paleontologists to come and assist.
However, as you and your team arrive at the site, you learn that the doctor left, seeking refuge from a sandstorm and accidentally exposing her coordinates to a competitive team of archaeologists. Satellite images of the area show that Dr. Tillman’s team is only an hour away from the dig site. You must now race to Dr. Harding’s campsite, uncover the clues in her pit, and bring forth the discovery before Dr. Arthur Tillman and his team arrive to stake claim of this historic find.
